{"tid":597580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[歌頌習帝之歌] 牢不可破的國家","createTime":"2018-03-18T18:18:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-18T23:52:28.000Z","uid":24140,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c50e9a087ba8b6b71686a668772d9bd27a1a4dbc","tid":597580,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T18:18:39.000Z","msg":"偉大共產黨，永久的國家；<br />\n人民之意志，自由結合成。<br />\n民族之意志，建立的中國，<br />\n統一而強大，萬年萬萬年！<br />\n自由的祖國，你無比光輝：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n各人民友愛的堅固堡壘！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n習主席的黨，人民的力量，<br />\n把我們引向共產主義勝利。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自由的陽光，照耀著我們；<br />\n偉大的習近平，指明了前程。<br />\n因正義之故，他領導人民，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n并激勵我們，去建立功勛。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自由的祖國，你無比光輝：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n各人民友愛的堅固堡壘！<br />\n習近平的黨，人民的力量，<br />\n把我們引向共產主義勝利。<br />\n<br />\n在共產主義的不朽勝利中，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我們看到親愛祖國的未來。<br />\n為了她那飄揚的鮮紅旗帜，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我們永遠忠誠無私地屹立。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自由的祖國，你無比光輝：<br />\n各人民友愛的堅固堡壘！<br />\n習近平的黨，人民的力量，<br />\n把我們引向共產主義勝利。"},{"pid":"7d199ce47f17acd63c6960876284b0a8cec949ff","tid":597580,"uid":27146,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T18:22:42.000Z","msg":"邊間教會"},{"pid":"f64ba6776ed459b39e4304ba8dc0cacbf129a48c","tid":597580,"uid":49136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T18:23:15.000Z","msg":"吾皇萬歲萬歲萬萬歲"},{"pid":"087b18668312a3dbee480fe7ab49f33e72294658","tid":597580,"uid":41243,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T18:29:58.000Z","msg":"Партия Си Цзиньпина - сила народная <img src=\"/assets